com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy
  • Enclosing class:
    ServiceProperties

    public static class ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy
extends java.lang.Object
    This inner class represents the retention policy settings for logging or metrics on the Queue service of the storage account. These settings include whether a retention policy is enabled for the data, and the number of days that metrics or logging data should be retained.

    • Method Detail

      • getDays

        public java.lang.Integer getDays()
        Gets the number of days that metrics or logging data should be retained. All data older than this value will be deleted. The value may be null if a retention policy is not enabled.
        Returns:
        The number of days that metrics or logging data should be retained.

      • setDays

        public ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy setDays(java.lang.Integer days)
        Sets the number of days that metrics or logging data should be retained. All data older than this value will be deleted. The value must be in the range from 1 to 365. This value must be set if a retention policy is enabled, but is not required if a retention policy is not enabled.
        Parameters:
        days - The number of days that metrics or logging data should be retained.
        Returns:
        A reference to this ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy instance.

      • isEnabled

        public boolean isEnabled()
        Gets a flag indicating whether a retention policy is enabled for the storage service.
        Returns:
        true if data retention is enabled, otherwise false.

      • setEnabled

        public ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy setEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Sets a flag indicating whether a retention policy is enabled for the storage service.
        Parameters:
        enabled - Set true to enable data retention.
        Returns:
        A reference to this ServiceProperties.RetentionPolicy instance.
